snippet.title: Tether Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Tether is officially available for Mac and Windows on Steam!
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2613510/Tether/

Grab your friends, and some rocks, in Tether: the BEST multiplayer rock-climbing platformer in the world (because it's the only one. But hey it's still super fun okay?).

Thanks for the music from this amazing person:
"I Got a Stick Arr Bryan Teoh" Kevin MacLeod (incompetech.com)
